## Edge Functions ‚Äî flussi reali

### Pairing PC sala (cloud)

```
Admin SPA ‚Üí pair-init (JWT)        ‚Üí INSERT pairing_codes (code 6 cifre, expires 10 min)
                                   ‚Üê {code: '123456', expires_at}
[Mostra codice all'utente]
PC sala  ‚Üí pair-claim (no auth)    ‚Üí SELECT pairing_codes by code ‚Üí INSERT paired_devices
                                       (con pair_token_hash = sha256(random_bytes(32)))
                                     UPDATE pairing_codes SET consumed_at = NOW()
                                   ‚Üê {device_token: '<random-32-byte-hex>', room_state: {...}}
PC sala  ‚Üí room-player-bootstrap   ‚Üí ogni 12-60s (Sprint A playback_mode tuning)
        (device_token)             ‚Üê {presentation_versions, network_mode, agent LAN, manifest}
```

### Pairing LAN-direct (Sprint N ‚Äî admin desktop ‚Üî sala desktop)

```
Admin Tauri  ‚Üí cmd_discover_lan_pcs(role='sala') ‚Üí mDNS browse 1500ms
                                                  ‚Üí [{name, addresses, port, txt}]
Admin SPA    ‚Üí genera codice 6 cifre client-side
Admin Tauri  ‚Üí pair_direct_lan({targetBaseUrl})  ‚Üí POST http://<sala>:<port>/functions/v1/pair-direct
                                                    body: {code, device_name, event_id, room_id}
Sala server  ‚Üí valida codice (window 5s) ‚Üí INSERT paired_devices LOCALE
                                            persisti device.json
                                          ‚Üê {device_token, paired_devices: {...}}
Admin Tauri  ‚Üí registerPairedDeviceOnAdminLocal ‚Üí POST /rest/v1/paired_devices LOCALE admin
                                                  (mirror per fan-out futuro)
```

### GDPR export (Sprint 7)

```
Admin SPA ‚Üí gdpr-export (JWT admin) ‚Üí RPC public.gdpr_export_tenant_data(tenant_id)
                                       (SECURITY DEFINER, bypassa RLS solo per export)
                                     ZIP service-role: events.json + rooms.json + sessions.json
                                       + presentations.json + audit.json
                                     UPLOAD su Storage path tenants/<id>/exports/<timestamp>.zip
